%!PS

%	This example appears in section "Filling Multiple Rectangles"
%	in Chapter 2 - "Paths and Painting".
%
%	Caveats:	Requires PostScript Level 2.

/inch { 72 mul } def			%  define inch procedure
0.1 setgray 1 inch 1.0 inch 3 inch 3 inch rectfill
0.3 setgray 2 inch 2.5 inch 3 inch 3 inch rectfill
0.5 setgray 3 inch 4.0 inch 3 inch 3 inch rectfill
0.7 setgray 4 inch 5.5 inch 3 inch 3 inch rectfill
0.9 setgray 5 inch 7.0 inch 3 inch 3 inch rectfill
showpage				%  display page
